{"id": 57851, "date": "2025-07-31T04:00:17", "date_gmt": "2025-07-31T11:00:17", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=57851"}, "modified": "2026-03-12T12:37:39", "modified_gmt": "2026-03-12T19:37:39", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-july-31-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/07/31/kingdom-of-days-july-31-2/", "title": {"rendered": "July 31"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1973:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band headline the first two shows of a three-night/six-show stand at My Father&#8217;s Place in Roslyn, New York. WLIR-FM broadcasts the late show live.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/0FxHJBVKI2g?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/hyHvurRWvX0?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1978:\u00a0</strong>The Darkness Tour continues its southern swing, arriving in Columbia, South Carolina, for a show at the Township Auditorium.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"52815\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/the_columbia_record_1978_08_01_30/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The_Columbia_Record_1978_08_01_30-scaled.jpg?fit=2560%2C2426&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2560,2426\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"The_Columbia_Record_1978_08_01_30\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The_Columbia_Record_1978_08_01_30-scaled.jpg?fit=300%2C284&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The_Columbia_Record_1978_08_01_30-scaled.jpg?fit=758%2C718&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-52815 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The_Columbia_Record_1978_08_01_30-scaled.jpg?resize=758%2C718&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"718\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The_Columbia_Record_1978_08_01_30-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The_Columbia_Record_1978_08_01_30-scaled.jpg?resize=300%2C284&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The_Columbia_Record_1978_08_01_30-scaled.jpg?resize=1024%2C970&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The_Columbia_Record_1978_08_01_30-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C728&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The_Columbia_Record_1978_08_01_30-scaled.jpg?w=1516&amp;ssl=1 1516w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The_Columbia_Record_1978_08_01_30-scaled.jpg?w=2274&amp;ssl=1 2274w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"3286\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1978-0731/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1978-0731.jpg?fit=351%2C600&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"351,600\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1978-0731\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1978-0731.jpg?fit=176%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1978-0731.jpg?fit=351%2C600&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-3286 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1978-0731.jpg?resize=351%2C600&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"351\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1978-0731.jpg?w=351&amp;ssl=1 351w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1978-0731.jpg?resize=176%2C300&amp;ssl=1 176w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 351px) 100vw, 351px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1982:\u00a0</strong>Bruce makes a guest appearance with Sonny Kenn and the Wild Ideas at Big Man&#8217;s West in Red Bank.</p>\n<div id=\"v-lzcXNflW-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/lzcXNflW?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>1984: </strong>&#8220;Cover Me&#8221; is released as the second single off of the red-hot\u00a0<em>Born in the U.S.A. </em>album. It will peak at #7 on the charts.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/s3tqIk8TPWM?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p>That evening, Bruce tour premieres &#8220;Growin&#8217; Up&#8221; at Night Two in Detroit on the Born in the U.S.A. Tour.</p>\n<div id=\"v-1IZ822FI-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/1IZ822FI?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20019\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1984-07-31/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1984-07-31.png?fit=2079%2C786&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2079,786\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1984-07-31\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1984-07-31.png?fit=300%2C113&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1984-07-31.png?fit=758%2C286&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20019 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1984-07-31.png?resize=758%2C287&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"287\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1984-07-31.png?w=2079&amp;ssl=1 2079w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1984-07-31.png?resize=300%2C113&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1984-07-31.png?resize=1024%2C387&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1984-07-31.png?resize=768%2C290&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1984-07-31.png?resize=1536%2C581&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1984-07-31.png?resize=2048%2C774&amp;ssl=1 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1987:\u00a0</strong>Bruce guest-stars with Marshall Crenshaw at The Stone Pony in Asbury Park for &#8220;You Can&#8217;t Sit Down,&#8221; &#8220;La Bamba,&#8221; and &#8220;Twist and Shout.&#8221;</p>\n<div id=\"v-91vNP1rr-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/91vNP1rr?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20020\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1987-07-31a/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1987-07-31a.png?fit=1589%2C1746&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1589,1746\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1987-07-31a\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1987-07-31a.png?fit=273%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1987-07-31a.png?fit=758%2C833&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20020 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1987-07-31a.png?resize=758%2C833&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"833\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1987-07-31a.png?w=1589&amp;ssl=1 1589w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1987-07-31a.png?resize=273%2C300&amp;ssl=1 273w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1987-07-31a.png?resize=932%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 932w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1987-07-31a.png?resize=768%2C844&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1987-07-31a.png?resize=1398%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1398w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1987-07-31a.png?w=1516&amp;ssl=1 1516w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20021\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1987-07-31b/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1987-07-31b.png?fit=1166%2C1748&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1166,1748\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1987-07-31b\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1987-07-31b.png?fit=200%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1987-07-31b.png?fit=683%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20021 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1987-07-31b.png?resize=758%2C1136&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1136\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1987-07-31b.png?w=1166&amp;ssl=1 1166w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1987-07-31b.png?resize=200%2C300&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1987-07-31b.png?resize=683%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 683w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1987-07-31b.png?resize=768%2C1151&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1987-07-31b.png?resize=1025%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1025w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1992:\u00a0</strong>The opening stand of World Tour 1992 reaches its midpoint in East Rutherford on Night Six of eleven. Many tour premieres tonight, including &#8220;Atlantic City,&#8221; &#8220;Spirit in the Night,&#8221; &#8220;I&#8217;m on Fire&#8221;, and the live debuts of &#8220;Pony Boy&#8221; and &#8220;Cross My Heart.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/xeSRlWZq2lk?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/zESafYXuPiM?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2001:\u00a0</strong>Bruce makes a surprise guest appearance at the Count Basie Theater in Red Bank, joining Bruce Hornsby for the final encore of &#8220;Cadillac Ranch.&#8221;</p>\n<div id=\"v-EQ77Afpd-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/EQ77Afpd?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>2005:\u00a0</strong>Bruce plays a stunning acoustic show in Columbus, playing &#8220;Lift Me Up&#8221; for the first time ever, and tour premiering &#8220;Cynthia&#8221; and &#8220;Back in Your Arms.&#8221; This show is available as part of Bruce&#8217;s official archive series, and it&#8217;s a wonderful listen.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/OjCUV60okiU?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/NrcrMsQFZUs?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/X3vsHrhBj8A?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/QrVQgy5M0CY?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/1dxrMGt2jsg?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/vdZ12-Y7_pU?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2008:\u00a0</strong>At the final of three Giants Stadium shows on the Magic Tour, Bruce tour premieres &#8220;Pretty Flamingo&#8221; and &#8220;Jersey Girl&#8221; and holds a mini-Seeger Sessions reunion when\u00a0Jeremy Chatzky, Sam Bardfeld, and Curtis King join the band for &#8220;American Land.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/y1Pht9wCmdc?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2012:\u00a0</strong>Bruce wraps up the first European leg of the Wrecking Ball Tour with a marathon of a show in Helsinki&#8211;his longest ever, over four hours&#8211;and that&#8217;s not even including a five-song pre-show! Five songs have their tour premieres, including &#8220;Back in Your Arms&#8221;, &#8220;Detroit Medley,&#8221; and covers of &#8220;I Don&#8217;t Want to Go Home,&#8221; &#8220;Rockin&#8217; All Over the World,&#8221; and &#8220;(Your Love Keeps Lifting Me) Higher and Higher.&#8221;\u00a0 Plus: rare outings for &#8220;Loose Ends,&#8221; &#8220;Be True,&#8221; &#8220;Light of Day,&#8221; and more&#8211;an absolutely amazing show. No surprise that it&#8217;s part of Bruce&#8217;s official archive series.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/b6wPi_h9O7k?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/3CsNsRkjx-s?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/u3pecVyDjpQ?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/MubovyHYDEc?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/j-y6vgOWL-g?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/c987UHFfyqs?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/XL8zzE3G-Ls?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/kOAjh5yFM4w?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2015:\u00a0</strong>Bruce makes a surprise guest appearance with U2 at the band&#8217;s gig at Madison Square Garden, joining them for &#8220;I Still Haven&#8217;t Found What I&#8217;m Looking For&#8221; and &#8220;Stand By Me.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/IR2y_Hjzmy8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20022\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2015-07-31/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2015-07-31.png?fit=659%2C1403&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"659,1403\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_ti